'''Aracáno''' is a [[Quenya]] name meaning "High Chieftain", being the [[amilessë]] of [[Fingolfin]]. In turn he gave it to his youngest son, which had the name [[Sindarized]] as '''''[[Argon]]'''''.<ref name=Shibboleth>{{PM|XINotes}}, p. 360. Cf. also p. 345</ref> 

==Etymology==
It is the combination of ''[[ara]]'' ("high") + ''[[cáno]]'' ("chieftain").<ref name=Shibboleth/>
